{"word":"H2623 - חָסִיד - châçîyd - khaw-seed' - Godly","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָסִיד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châçîyd"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-seed'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Godly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பரிசுத்தமான, தயவுள்ளவரான, பக்தியுள்ளவனான, கிருபையுள்ளவரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"faithful, kind, godly, holy one, saint, pious"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H2616 - חָסַד - châçad - khaw-sad'/2616\">H2616</a>; properly <i>kind</i>, that is, (religiously) <i>pious</i> (a saint): - godly (man), good, holy (one), merciful, saint, [un-] godly."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2616 - חָסַד - châçad - khaw-sad'/2616\">H2616</a>, <a href=\"#/H2617 - חֵסֵד - chêçêd - kheh'-sed/2617\">H2617</a>, <a href=\"#/H2619 - חֲסַדְיָה - Chăçadyâh - khas-ad-yaw'/2619\">H2619</a>, <a href=\"#/H2623 - חָסִיד - châçîyd - khaw-seed'/2623\">H2623</a>, <a href=\"#/H2624 - חֲסִידָה - chăçîydâh - khas-ee-daw'/2624\">H2624</a>"}]}